1. Install JDK-8

 sudo apt-get remove openjdk*
 sudo apt update
 sudo apt install openjdk-8-jdk openjdk-8-jre


2.Download MPJ Express and extract in the Downloads dir



3. Install Apache Netbeans

 sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade
 sudo snap install netbeans --classic


Glassfish server version must be 4.1.1



//how to install mpj in ubuntu->

1. Install Java Development Kit (JDK):
2. Download MPJ Express:
3. Extract the downloaded file:   unzip mpj-v0_44.zip
4. Set up environment variables:   export MPJ_HOME=/path/to/mpj
                                                  export PATH=$MPJ_HOME/bin:$PATH
5. Verify Installation:      mpjrun.sh -h